0C1F7A21.Line13.B20BA: Man or beast who took it, the Goose isn’t the same without it.

2AFD8914.Line7.B20BA: In their hurry they left blood on the steps. Amateurs.

91090F92.Line5.B20BA: Aye. Torn right off the hooks.
